00:41:43.926 --> 00:41:47.419
1940.

00:41:47.419 --> 00:41:49.415
1940.

00:41:49.415 --> 00:41:51.411
1940.

00:41:51.411 --> 00:41:52.409
On my birthday.

00:42:11.371 --> 00:42:12.868
The Germans walked in.

00:42:22.349 --> 00:42:23.846
Walked into Holland.

00:42:27.339 --> 00:42:28.836
- Germans invaded Hungary.

00:42:39.315 --> 00:42:40.812
I was in second grade.

00:42:53.287 --> 00:42:54.784
I had a teacher.

00:42:58.277 --> 00:43:01.770
I had a teacher,
a very tall man,

00:43:01.770 --> 00:43:04.265
his hair was completely
